data.description: Gorgeous custom home by R E Signature sits on a huge 9,167 sq ft corner lot. Exquisite home features 4 bdrms 2.5 baths, spectacular kitchen walk-in pantry, gas cook top. Open concept to living & dining room. Illuminated coffered ceilings throughout. Master suite has large bathroom & magnificent closet which is a room of it's own. 4th bdrm is currently used as workspace (no pics) Equipped with outdoor kitchen, front & back sprinklers, outdoor shed & solar panels for energy efficiency NO ELECTRICITY BILL!
